data.title: Asking For Trouble
data.meta_description: Nothing against Christian Slater, but who doesn't look at this movie ad quote and think the missing words are "is not"? If you run a quote with a gaping hole like that, many people are going to fill it in with the worst options possible.
data.text:
LinkedIn and 3rd parties use essential and non-essential cookies to provide, secure, analyze and improve our Services, and to show you relevant ads (including professional and job ads) on and off LinkedIn. Learn more in our Cookie Policy.

Select Accept to consent or Reject to decline non-essential cookies for this use. You can update your choices at any time in your settings.

Nothing against Christian Slater, but who doesn't look at this movie ad quote and think the missing words are "is not"? If you run a quote with a gaping hole like that, many people are going to fill it in with the worst options possible.
